    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained by its previous owners. The engine starts promptly and runs smoothly, while the transmission provides reliable, predictable shifting for both city and highway driving. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of major wear, though you may find minor cosmetic imperfections on the exterior consistent with careful regular use. All major systems are fully functional, making this a dependable and attractive choice for anyone seeking a quality pre-owned vehicle.",
      "price": 35500.0,
