    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a distinguished vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and aesthetic discipline. This unit has been maintained to rigorous standards, ensuring a driving experience characterized by both performance and consistency. The interior remains refined, and the exterior reflects the meticulous care of professional ownership. For the discerning driver who values reliability and proven quality, this offering represents an exceptional acquisition.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking to find a new home for this absolute beauty. It\u2019s been a total joy to drive and has been super well-maintained over the years. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014runs like a dream and looks great, with just enough character to show it\u2019s been loved! If you're looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next road trip, you've found it. Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come see it in person! \u2728",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies. This unit features a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under high lateral loads. The suspension retains its factory geometry with refreshed bushings, providing the tactile feedback these chassis are known for. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain remains robust with consistent compression across all cylinders and precise valve clearances.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Reliable performance. Regular maintenance history. Clean title. Minor cosmetic wear. Ready for immediate use.",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. Finished in a deep Midnight Metallic Blue, the exterior retains a brilliant shine, though a close inspection will reveal a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, professionally touched-up scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel arch. The body remains perfectly straight with no history of accidents. Inside, the Charcoal leather interior has been treated with care; the bolsters show only light natural creasing, and the cabin remains free of any odors or stains. Every feature\u2014from the panoramic sunroof to the heated seating and navigation system\u2014operates flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is in its prime. I have maintained a rigorous service schedule, including a recent transmission fluid flush and a fresh set of high-performance all-season tires. It starts quietly, accelerates smoothly, and offers a firm, responsive ride that feels like it belongs on the open road. This is a complete, turn-key package for a buyer who values a well-documented and honest service history.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably maintained vehicle, which serves as a testament to engineering durability and refined automotive design. This specimen has been curated for the driver who demands a harmonious balance of performance and sophisticated presentation. Thoroughly inspected to ensure operational excellence, the vehicle exhibits consistent mechanical integrity and a well-preserved interior. This offering represents a distinguished acquisition for those seeking premium quality and proven reliability in their next automotive investment.",
      "price": 36450.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    }
